name: Crossing the event horizon
description:
Generative animation by outerground.
Imagine falling into a black hole, being infinitely elongated, stripped atom by atom, pared back down to raw information.. nature's ulimate recycle. what if that information carries memory and eventually emanates when a BH gets full up & pop; a singularity creates a new branch of separate spacetime within the old universe. Universe Evolution perhaps on unimaginable metatimescales
